column6: Is there mitochondria present in the whole of the axonal bundle?
column7: Do all the branches have mitochondria?
column10: Is there scrunching/curving of the leg?
column12: Does the axonal bundle split or thin at any time or are there chunks missing?
column13: Is the distal end of the axonal bundle organized?
column15: Is the branching straight - following the pattern of the axonal bundle?
column16: Are there branches in all aspects of the femur?
